#: ../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.14/site-packages/psycopg/types/composite.py:docstring
#: of psycopg.types.composite.register_composite:11
msgid ""
"optional function that will be used when loading a composite type from the "
"database if the Python type is not a sequence compatible with the composite "
